WEBVTT

00:07:00.835 --> 00:07:03.376
The traffic jam is awful
in Tokyo, as you know.

00:07:03.376 --> 00:07:04.528
(Laughter)

00:07:04.528 --> 00:07:09.379
The driver in front,
she needs to learn how to drive.

00:07:09.379 --> 00:07:11.910
Now these days,

00:07:11.910 --> 00:07:16.530
kids need a small dosage of danger.

00:07:18.970 --> 00:07:21.375
And in this kind of occasion,

00:07:21.375 --> 00:07:25.300
they learn to help each other.

00:07:25.300 --> 00:07:29.735
This is society. This is the kind of
opportunity we are losing these days.